description: Korean Street Food- Fast and Sassy. Find us on the streets of Columbus OH serving everything from Hodduk to Kimbop.Bringing a taste of Seoul to Columbus, Ajumama serves Korean street food without the 7000 mile road trip. Always fresh and sassy, sometimes sweet or hot, a lot of traditional with a little rock and roll, but way more than just BBQ or kimchi.  We can’t wait to take you on a culinary tour of Korea, unlike anything else you will find in central Ohio and share our love and passion for Korean food with you.Here comes Ajumama!
name: Ajumama
